---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Terms of Service - CALENDHUB"
  description="Terms of Service for CALENDHUB AI-powered visual creation platform."
>
  <div class="min-h-screen bg-background">
    <div class="container max-w-4xl mx-auto py-16 px-4">
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-display font-bold text-text mb-8">Terms of Service</h1>

        <p class="text-text-muted text-lg mb-8">Last updated: {new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-US', { year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric' })}</p>

        <div class="space-y-8 text-text">
          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold mb-4">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
            <p class="mb-4">
              By accessing and using CALENDHUB ("Service"), you accept and agree to be bound by the terms and provision of this agreement. If you do not agree to abide by the above, please do not use this service.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold mb-4">2. Service Description</h2>
            <p class="mb-4">
              CALENDHUB is an AI-powered visual creation platform that enables users to generate, edit, and enhance images and videos using artificial intelligence technology. Our services include but are not limited to:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 space-y-2">
              <li>AI image generation from text prompts</li>
              <li>Image-to-image transformations</li>
              <li>Video generation and editing</li>
              <li>Custom model training (LoRa)</li>
              <li>Background replacement and object removal</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold mb-4">3. User Accounts</h2>
            <p class="mb-4">
              To access certain features of the Service, you must register for an account. You agree to:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 space-y-2">
              <li>Provide accurate and complete registration information</li>
              <li>Maintain the security of your account credentials</li>
              <li>Notify us immediately of any unauthorized access to your account</li>
              <li>Be responsible for all activities that occur under your account</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold mb-4">4. Acceptable Use</h2>
            <p class="mb-4">You agree not to use the Service to:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 space-y-2">
              <li>Generate illegal, harmful, or offensive content</li>
              <li>Create deepfakes or misleading content without proper disclosure</li>
              <li>Infringe on intellectual property rights of others</li>
              <li>Generate content depicting minors in inappropriate contexts</li>
              <li>Attempt to reverse engineer or compromise our AI models</li>
              <li>Use the service for spam or malicious activities</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold mb-4">5. Content and Intellectual Property</h2>
            <p class="mb-4">
              You retain ownership of content you upload to our Service. By using our Service, you grant us a license to process your content for the purpose of providing our services. Content generated by our AI models is owned by you, subject to these terms and applicable law.
            </p>
            <p class="mb-4">
              Our AI models, algorithms, and platform technology remain our intellectual property. You may not attempt to extract, copy, or reverse engineer our proprietary technology.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold mb-4">6. Subscription and Payment</h2>
            <p class="mb-4">
              Some features of our Service require payment. Subscription fees are charged in advance and are generally non-refundable. Once you use any tokens or resources provided with your subscription, no refunds will be issued. For detailed information about our refund policies and specific circumstances, please refer to our Refund & Cancellation Policy. We reserve the right to change our pricing with 30 days notice to existing subscribers.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold mb-4">7. Token System</h2>
            <p class="mb-4">
              Our Service operates on a token-based system where certain actions consume tokens. For active subscribers, unused tokens accumulate month after month and do not expire as long as your subscription remains active. Unused tokens do not carry monetary value and cannot be refunded or transferred to other accounts.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold mb-4">8. Service Availability</h2>
            <p class="mb-4">
              While we strive for high availability, we do not guarantee that our Service will be available 100% of the time. We may temporarily suspend access for maintenance, updates, or other operational reasons.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold mb-4">9. Limitation of Liability</h2>
            <p class="mb-4">
              CALENDHUB shall not be liable for any indirect, incidental, special, consequential, or punitive damages resulting from your use of the Service. Our total liability to you for any damages shall not exceed the amount you paid for the Service in the 12 months preceding the claim.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold mb-4">10. Privacy</h2>
            <p class="mb-4">
              Your privacy is important to us. Please review our Privacy Policy, which governs how we collect, use, and protect your personal information.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold mb-4">11. Termination</h2>
            <p class="mb-4">
              We may terminate your access to the Service at any time for violation of these terms. You may terminate your account at any time through your account settings. Upon termination, your right to use the Service ceases immediately.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold mb-4">12. Changes to Terms</h2>
            <p class="mb-4">
              We reserve the right to modify these terms at any time. We will notify users of material changes via email or through the Service. Continued use of the Service after changes constitutes acceptance of the new terms.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold mb-4">13. Governing Law</h2>
            <p class="mb-4">
              These terms are governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of Albania. Any disputes arising under these terms shall be subject to the exclusive jurisdiction of the courts in Albania.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold mb-4">14. Contact Information</h2>
            <p class="mb-4">
              If you have any questions about these Terms of Service, please contact us at:
            </p>
            <div class="bg-border/30 p-6 rounded-lg">
              <p class="mb-2"><strong>Email:</strong> contact@calendhub.com</p>
              <p><strong>Response Time:</strong> We aim to respond within 48 hours</p>
            </div>
          </section>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>